/*REXX*/                             
SAY "BMI CALCULATOR"                 
SAY "WHAT IS YOUR WEIGHT? (POUNDS)"  
PULL WEIGHT                          
SAY "WHAT IS YOUR HEIGHT?(INCHES)"   
PULL HEIGHT                          
SQRH = HEIGHT * HEIGHT               
BMI = WEIGHT /SQRH * 703             
SAY "YOUR BMI IS: " BMI              
IF BMI < 18.5 THEN                   
 SAY "YOU ARE UNDERWEIGHT"           
IF BMI > 18.5 & BMI <= 25 THEN       
 SAY "YOU ARE HEALTHY WEIGHT"        
IF BMI > 25 & BMI <=29.9  THEN       
 SAY "YOU ARE OVERWEITH"             
IF BMI > 30 THEN                     
 SAY "YOU ARE OBESE"                 